                                record-audio-app

app for recording and visualizing audio.

usage: record-audio.py [-h] [-r RECORD] [-d DURATION] [-v VISUALIZE]
                       [-s SIN_FREQUENCY] [-w WINDOW_LENGTH] [-o OVERLAP]

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -r RECORD, --record RECORD
                        record audio and save it to a file
  -d DURATION, --duration DURATION
                        duration of the recording in seconds
  -v VISUALIZE, --visualize VISUALIZE
                        visualize audio file
  -s SIN_FREQUENCY, --sin-frequency SIN_FREQUENCY
                        frequency of the sinusoid
  -w WINDOW_LENGTH, --window-length WINDOW_LENGTH
                        window length in seconds for the stdft
  -o OVERLAP, --overlap OVERLAP
                        window proportion overlap for the stdft
